modShortDescription: This mod replaces the dropped backpack model with the weapons bag one.
modDescription:
This mod replaces the dropped [backpack](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-backpack/) model with the weapons bag one.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Snufki-n/Snufkin_Modlets/tree/master/Snufkin_BiggerBackpackDrop)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/18673-snufkins-assorted-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Snufkin](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/snufkin/)
